Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maurer, you haven't been\Ntaking a bath, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised, when I moved\Nto the desk next to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'd take one every other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor\Nin the reception office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home,\Nso make your own tea, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor? At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had a bath, either.\NHe smells almost as bad as you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?\NUpsy daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is it that\NI haven't been able to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't realize that she's able to\Nmake a living at this paper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,with no future,\Nthanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... My name is Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for your assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... He really is filthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you're a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Doctor,\Nis this what you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The next target of the person\Nwho's been killing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,middle-aged couples\Nthroughout Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is here in Heidelberg?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That couple is fostering a young girl,\Nand when that girl turns 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.99,0:01:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the killer will come to take her away...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he does, the foster parents\Nare sure to be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have no idea\Nwho that girl or her foster parents are,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or where they live...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not delusional,\NI don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke. Please believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! Not even the gossip rags\Nwould write up that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here\Nto get you to write it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After those twins\Nslipped out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there is at least\Na 6-month blank period
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,before the brother showed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that,\Nafter leaving the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,those twins came to\NHeidelberg together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And the two were raised by\Nthe girl's current foster parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But the brother ran away from here\Nafter a short period,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving his sister behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you write a novel?\N'Course it probably won't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that there is\Na missing person's report out on the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And there might even be\Na newspaper article about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me check the newspapers\Nfrom nine years ago! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't allow\Nany more people to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The president has a thing against\Ncomputerization, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,These are smaller versions\Nof the daily newspapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and manuscript files.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are files\Nof cancelled stories and raw data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Japanese bow?\NYou're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't have the time\Nto spend on silly stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and leave\Nwhen you're satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Every once in a while,\NI get a nut case like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please let me find something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.97,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}The Missing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.\NYou're looking well, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fainting like that...\NYou startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you really didn't like\Nthe boy we hooked you up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I just suddenly felt bad.\NI have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.\NYou don't have to worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That Otto... When I talked to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out that he's not\Nyour "prince on a white horse."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he didn't send you\Nany email message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you fainted\Nbecause you saw that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I only saw him for a second,\Nso I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your impression of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt very nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not it...\NI can't explain it well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't force yourself, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to put it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it felt just like\Nwhen I had that nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Absolute evil"...\NIt's beginning to sound religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't go to a church...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it seems to me that\Neverything will be cleared up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if I see that person again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel that you will regain\Nthe memory you've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one means you may be\Nable to employ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think you should let that\Nbe a burden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about your future\Nwithout stressing, is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just work up a sweat\Nplaying sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and your insecurities\Nshould disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maurer, pull another all-nighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, were you the one\Nwho let that guy use the file room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I asked him\Nwhat he was doing there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and he said\Nyou had given him permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean he's still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! It's about time you... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Hey! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, isn't it?\NI always have breakfast here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you go home?\NWhat about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't got one.\NMy wife left me, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always so busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I finally realized it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,my wife had gone back to her parents\Nwith our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought about\Nbringing your wife home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who walked out!\NWhy should I go to get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you seem to regret\Nbeing so occupied with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Work is most important to a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Any wife who cannot understand that\Nis welcome to leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It was none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NIt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You smoke too much.\NI say that as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit saying the same thing\Nmy wife said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife was worried\Nabout your health, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I finally finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Her sweaters used to be\Nthis tiny before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, are you really going to tell her\Nthat she's not really our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we leave it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...\NThere's no need to tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is our daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy... am I hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gaitel may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:11:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow, your birthday, let's meet at\NHeidelberg Castle at 7:00 PM."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow... at Heidelberg Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so busy, but here I am staring at\Na mountain of papers with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If... it's just a thought, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to go to get my wife...\NDo you think she'd come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If you quit smoking, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,11-year-old boy disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that he was kidnapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but there has been no word\Nfrom a kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,16 Necker Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone named Fortner has filled out\Na missing person's report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The raw data should be\Nin here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that that killer would
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,come to take his sister away\Nwhen she turned 20, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If the boy in this article\Nis her brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! His birth date is printed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the 20th birthday\Nof those twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello, Dad? It's me.\NI just finished work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet up with a friend\Nthen I'll be coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... At Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is making preparations\Nfor a birthday party, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She says she's going to meet\Na friend before coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's all grown up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe this will help me\Nto remember things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what do you intend to do if\Nthe twin girl is at the Fortners' home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case,\Nthat family is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will contact the police\Nand ask for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the police will\Ndo anything just from your reasoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late\Nafter something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to happen.\NIt's all in your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doctor...\NOf the four murder cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself went to\Nthe crime scene in Cologne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something different\Nabout that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed no purpose,\Nno greed, no bitterness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like someone simply ended\Nthese people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell just by looking\Nat the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that a kid\Nwho wasn't even 20, did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you think a youngster could kill\Nthose people without feeling any emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't something done by a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't find the right words\Nto describe this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to describe it, it's trite,\Nbut that was the Devil's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If that killer were to appear before me,\NI would kill him without a pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,16 Necker Street... We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!\NSorry to call on you so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you.\NI'm Maurer of the Heidelberg Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What would a newspaper reporter\Nbe wanting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'd like to ask you\Nsome questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's regarding this missing persons report\Nthat you filed in 1986...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can forget about that matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Could you please talk to us?\NDon't you have a girl living with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The twin sister of\Nthe boy who disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a birthday cake prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You took in a pair of twins\Nnine years ago, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl still lives with you,\Ndoesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have raised her\Nas our true daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't make waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You took in a pair of twins\Nnine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy had surgical scars\Non his head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the girl had amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner, you must contact\Nthe police at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lives, and your daughter's,\Nare in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us see your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She is out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was going\Nto meet a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me use your car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! We must\Nnotify the police first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the time\Nto explain things to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the key, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll call them from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! As I said earlier,\Nhe's a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back alive...\NThen I'll quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow the quack's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife will be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how should I explain\Nthis to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our daughter... Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NLet me use your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened to our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line's been cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... Please be safe... Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way past time...\NI guess that message was a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to... wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to make sure\Nyou waited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to wait...\NDon't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was told!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... No, you're Nina Fortner,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:20:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?\NI'm Dr. Tenma. I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. You must go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You... Are you...\Nmy prince on a white horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't butt in... Don't butt in, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gotta wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't, I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He said no one would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I need something to tie him up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he say he was coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He just said\Nhe would come here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,after doing something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to hurry back to your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later!\NWe've got to hurry, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Anna...\N- Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... I can't get loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:22:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me! Who are you?\NAnd I'm not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were brought into\Nmy hospital, you were Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:53.45,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}House of Tragedy
